abstract: Katie Ledecky wins 800-meter freestyle at Arena Pro Swim Series meet in Arizona; other swimming news noted.
lead_paragraph: Ledecky won the 800-meter freestyle by nearly 15 seconds at the Arena Pro Swim Series meet in Mesa, Ariz.

headline.main: Katie Ledecky Wins Her Third Race in Three Days
